lead_paragraph: Chris Owings had a career high-tying four hits, Jake Lamb homered, and the Arizona Diamondbacks beat the Colorado Rockies 9-4 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Owings, Lamb Lead Diamondbacks Past Rockies, 9-4
